Interface XmlByte

  • All Superinterfaces:
    XmlAnySimpleType, XmlDecimal, XmlInt, XmlInteger, XmlLong, XmlObject, XmlShort, XmlTokenSource

    XmlByteImpl
    public interface XmlByte
extends XmlShort
    Corresponds to the XML Schema xs:byte type.

    Naturally, convertible to Java byte.
